EN: My sister feeds the birds in the garden, she uses a bucket to hold food.

ZH: 小男孩喜欢踢翻水桶。
EN: The little boy likes to kick over the water bucket.

ZH: 桶里有一些虫子在爬。
EN: There are some bugs crawling in the bucket.

ZH: 他的海洋生物桶收藏了很多品种的贝壳。
EN: His marine life bucket collects many different types of seashells.

ZH: 这个木桶已经使用了五十年，但还是很结实。
EN: This wooden bucket has been in use for fifty years, but it is still very sturdy.
